      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. Best suited for someone seeking an inexpensive daily driver, a project, or a practical backup vehicle, it presents an affordable entry point with room to make it your own. An honest opportunity at a hard-to-find price point.",
