    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This car is a solid budget-friendly option that starts, runs, and offers a great chance for someone handy, a first-time buyer, or anyone needing simple transportation without spending big. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. If you want something approachable, honest, and full of potential, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and worth a look.",
