    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project opportunity with a tough-running powertrain and plenty of usable life for the right buyer. Starts, moves, and delivers the kind of straightforward mechanical feel that makes it a practical candidate for daily beater duty, light restoration, or parts-saving ownership. Cosmetic and age-related wear are present, but the vehicle still offers good utility, a complete package, and a platform with clear upside for someone willing to put in a little attention. If you want inexpensive transportation with project potential, this one is worth a look.",
