      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with unmistakable presence, this car has the kind of honest, well-lived character that turns errands into a story and a driveway into a conversation piece. It\u2019s the sort of machine for someone with vision\u2014an affordable way into a distinctive ride with plenty of personality and room to make it your own. If you\u2019ve been looking for a budget-friendly project, a practical runabout with soul, or simply something that stands apart from the anonymous crowd, this one brings charm, purpose, and possibility in equal measure.",
      "price": 6500.0,
